A1 Fruit water is extracted from real South African fruit and is available in three flavours – Mandarin, Lemon and Grapefruit. It has zero calories, is sugar free, and has no sweeteners or preservatives. A1 Fruit water is a by-product from making South African juice – keeping impact low, with their supply chain rooted in South Africa enabling a fair deal for all from farm-to-can.  A1 Fruit Water works with farming partners located in the sub-tropical mango and citrus producing region of Hoedspruit in the north of the country.  Every A1 Fruit Water you buy supports the South African economy – from farmers and factories to drivers and distributors. Currently packed in a 300ml slimline can, and wrapped in a sleeve (both are recyclable!). Add this delicious drink to your next grocery list and support local. You can find A1 Fruit Water at selected Pick n Pay’s, SPAR’s, on Takealot.com as well as independent retailers. A1 Fruit Water – Think South African Drink South African. Details:  A1 Fruit Water – Instagram, Facebook or visit their website www.a1fruitwater.com